subject: meson support: rename service files
commitMessage:
meson support: rename service files

Rename phosphor-fan service files from X.in to X.service. Previously
there had been a hard-coded BINDIR allowing configure-time control of
binary destination. This is not a requirement for obmc and therefore has
been removed and BINDIR replaced with /usr/bin.

Change-Id: I68f00910a6887a4c4fc658c2e40badab09613483
Signed-off-by: Mike Capps <mikepcapps@gmail.com>
